name: Frozen Faces
description:
When I walk in the forest on a freshly snowy day. I often look at things in a new way. How could one not? At the same time though, this contrast of a new coat on my surroundings often makes me remember things. Faces and memories that had been locked away- got second wind by the snow. I wonder if I am that face for somebody else.
Image size: 5376 x 3840
